These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, dancer
1. the musician is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the dancer is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | musician | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | folk | gospel |

